text: Sven Hanson (2 February 1892 - 22 June 1972) was a Swedish swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1892 births Category:1972 deaths Category:Swedish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Sweden Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kristinehamn Municipality Category:Swedish male breaststroke swimmers
